<p>My formula field to display image from user and default image is as follows:</p>  <p>IF( photouploader__HeightOfPhoto__c >0 &amp;&amp;  photouploader__WidthOfPhoto__c >0,IMAGE(photouploader__Image_URL__c, "Image",  photouploader__HeightOfPhoto__c ,  photouploader__WidthOfPhoto__c ), IMAGE("<a href="https://c.ap1.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.FileDownload?file=01590000009hzxd" rel="nofollow">https://c.ap1.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.FileDownload?file=01590000009hzxd</a>", "Image", 100 , 100))</p>